for Ramadan.

22:36.867 --> 22:39.934
- You came just to
give me the schedule?

22:40.000 --> 22:41.533
- Yes.

22:41.600 --> 22:43.300
- And there's nothing else?

22:50.467 --> 22:53.133
- I made an assumption
about the Reverend Cloutier,

22:53.200 --> 22:54.633
that he was a phony.

22:54.700 --> 22:56.033
- But he's not.

22:56.100 --> 22:58.834
- This all started when
Timmy Kirk decided to convert.

22:58.900 --> 23:00.500
