exactly the same thing.

23:55.066 --> 23:58.800
Father, I-I accused you of
being consumed with envy.

23:58.867 --> 24:00.433
- I was.

24:00.500 --> 24:03.800
- But I was, too.

24:03.867 --> 24:05.867
- Our sins are our bond.

24:07.934 --> 24:11.433
The house of God
has many rooms.

24:11.500 --> 24:14.100
If a person chooses to move
from one room to another,

24:14.166 --> 24:18.133
we who are left behind
must rest assured

24:18.200 --> 24:22.867
that the room that we're in
is not empty.

24:22.934 --> 24:25.033
God's presence
fills every room.

24:25.100 --> 24:29.333
God's love shines through
the entire house.

24:33.266 --> 24:35.200
Let us pray.

24:38.266 --> 24:41.166
- Currier and Ives.
Norman Rockwell.

24:41.233 --> 24:43.967
