always gets the answers.

32:23.500 --> 32:25.533
- Maybe you should
go on the show.

32:25.600 --> 32:27.066
- Yeah, right.

32:27.133 --> 32:28.867
"Hey, I'm Tobias Beecher.

32:28.934 --> 32:30.867
