33:06.500 --> 33:09.066
I knew I had to serve
minimally four years.

33:10.567 --> 33:11.934
But all things considered,
I figured my record

33:12.000 --> 33:13.200
would pretty much cancel out

33:13.266 --> 33:14.600
any chance of
getting released early.

33:14.667 --> 33:16.166
- Well, you may be right.

33:16.233 --> 33:19.867
But...I've reviewed
your case,

33:19.934 --> 33:22.667
and I think the extenuating
circumstances--

33:22.734 --> 33:25.000
