both your wife and son,

33:25.066 --> 33:28.834
your daughter,
her genuine need for you,

33:28.900 --> 33:32.000
your improved behavior
over the past six months,

33:32.066 --> 33:33.934
the commendations
from Sister Peter Marie

33:34.000 --> 33:35.600
and Dr. Nathan...

33:35.667 --> 33:38.800
might motivate the parole board
to look highly on you.

33:41.667 --> 33:43.567
They'll let you go free.

33:45.934 --> 33:47.533
- I...

33:52.567 --> 33:53.934
- Tobias?

33:57.900 --> 33:59.467
