53:33.600 --> 53:35.333
- Salah...

53:35.400 --> 53:37.834
you seem troubled.

53:37.900 --> 53:39.734
- My soul is heavy, minister.

53:39.800 --> 53:41.300
- So talk to me.

53:41.367 --> 53:42.934
- I'm afraid.

53:43.000 --> 53:44.700
Afraid to speak the truth.

53:44.767 --> 53:47.100
- Never be afraid of
the truth, my brother.

53:47.166 --> 53:49.834
- I lied to you.

53:49.900 --> 53:51.233
You see,
when I first approached you

53:51.300 --> 53:53.300
saying I wanted to
become a Muslim,

53:53.367 --> 53:57.000
I had vengeance in my heart...
'cause of what you did

53:57.066 --> 53:59.100
killing Adebisi.

53:59.166 --> 54:01.934
But then the bliss of Allah
replaced the vengeance,

54:02.000 --> 54:03.934
and now I'm a true believer.

54:04.000 --> 54:07.567
- I knew the day that
I embraced you,

54:07.633 --> 54:09.467
that you were lying.

54:09.533 --> 54:10.467
- You did?

54:10.533 --> 54:11.533
- Mm-hmm.

54:11.600 --> 54:13.867
- Then why?

54:13.934 --> 54:17.233
- The ways of the Almighty
are wondrous, indeed.

54:17.300 --> 54:20.800
He brought us together
at this time and this place

54:20.867 --> 54:23.433
so that we could
learn from each other.

54:23.500 --> 54:25.233
- You learn from me?

54:25.300 --> 54:26.734
How?

54:26.800 --> 54:30.200
- That day I went to Adebisi
and I swore my loyalty to him...

54:32.233 --> 54:36.400
Since his death, I've been
struggling with my demons.

54:36.467 --> 54:38.834
Still do.

54:38.900 --> 54:43.867
But you've taught me the world
has many possibilities.

54:44.967 --> 54:47.133
- Robson and Hoyt
want you dead.

54:47.200 --> 54:48.934
- I know.

54:49.000 --> 54:50.667
- What are we gonna do?

54:50.734 --> 54:52.934
- As with everything else...

54:54.500 --> 54:56.734
We'll leave this
in the hands of God.

55:04.367 --> 55:05.934
- If you take care of this,

55:06.000 --> 55:07.533
I'll bring you into
the brotherhood.

55:07.600 --> 55:08.834
- Fuck you, nigga!

55:08.900 --> 55:11.967
- If you don't...
I'll feed you to them.

55:16.133 --> 55:18.567
- I'm ready to do
whatever you need.

55:51.967 --> 55:54.333
- No!
No!

56:14.533 --> 56:15.700
- Imam.

56:19.500 --> 56:20.934
Salah is dead.

56:22.767 --> 56:24.533
- I killed him, you know.

56:27.100 --> 56:29.667
I killed him just like
I killed Adebisi.

56:33.300 --> 56:36.266
I might as well have had
the knife in my hand...

56:39.667 --> 56:41.533
In these bloody hands.

56:41.600 --> 56:42.867
- Kareem...

56:42.934 --> 56:45.000
- No.

56:45.066 --> 56:47.066
Say nothing.

56:47.133 --> 56:48.500
- But you can't
blame yourself.

56:48.567 --> 56:50.867
- Leave me,

56:50.934 --> 56:54.166
because my demons
need feeding.

56:56.333 --> 56:58.200
Leave me!

57:16.300 --> 57:18.900
- They say that every
snowflake is different,

57:18.967 --> 57:20.900
but how can they
really be sure?

57:20.967 --> 57:23.300
I mean, think about all
the snowflakes that have fallen

57:23.367 --> 57:26.300
all over the world
throughout Earth's history.

57:26.367 --> 57:28.400
Law of averages dictates
that at least two of them

57:28.467 --> 57:29.934
had to be similar.

57:30.000 --> 57:32.233
Like human beings,
like the men in Oz,

57:32.300 --> 57:34.734
even if
they start out unique,

57:34.800 --> 57:36.767
they end up the same.
